source.name: Final Decisions of the Trademark Trial and Appeal Board (TTAB)
source.description: Offers search, display, and download of Trademark Trial and Appeal Board (TTAB) Final Decisions. Search requires one or a combination of the following: Proceeding or Application number (default); Type of Case; Party or Parties; TTAB Panel (2); Issue; TTAB Decision; Opposer's or Petitioner's Marks and Goods or Services; Applicant's or Respondent's Marks and Goods or Services; Marks and Goods Cited by Examining Attorney; Examining Attorney; Citable as Precedent of TTAB; identifier; issue date; start date; end date; search document text (free form); records per page (60 default; 15; 30; 45; or all). Additionally, there is a link to retrieve the last 30 days of TTAB decisions. Format is PDF. Unavailable during daily database backups from 01:00 - 05:00 AM U.S. Eastern Time.
